createdAt.description: Timestamp indicating when the email complaint was created

campaignId.description: Unique identifier for the campaign associated with the email complaint data

itblInternal.description: Holds internal metadata related to the iterable data being accessed.

documentCreatedAt.description: Timestamp indicating when the internal document was created

documentUpdatedAt.description: Timestamp indicating when the internal document was last updated

messageId.description: Unique identifier for the email message associated with the complaint

templateId.description: Unique identifier for the email template used in the campaign

email.description: Email address of the recipient who lodged the complaint

userId.description: Unique identifier for the user who lodged the email complaint

recipientState.description: State or status of the recipient associated with the complaint
